#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:1
msgid "LinearFitResult"
msgstr "LinearFitResult"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:3
msgid "Definizione"
msgstr "Definition"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:5
msgid ""
"`LinearFitResult` e una `dataclass` immutabile con `slots=True`, usata come oggetto "
"di ritorno di [`lin_fit`](lin-fit.md)."
msgstr ""
"`LinearFitResult` is an immutable `dataclass` with `slots=True`, used as the return "
"object of [`lin_fit`](lin-fit.md)."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:7
msgid "Scopo"
msgstr "Purpose"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:9
msgid ""
"Raccogliere in un unico contenitore tipizzato i parametri del fit, le incertezze "
"associate, i residui, le diagnostiche e la figura opzionale."
msgstr ""
"Collect the fit parameters, associated uncertainties, residuals, diagnostics, and "
"optional figure in a single typed container."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:11
msgid "Campi"
msgstr "Fields"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:13
msgid "`slope`: pendenza della retta stimata."
msgstr "`slope`: slope of the fitted line."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:14
msgid "`intercept`: intercetta della retta stimata."
msgstr "`intercept`: intercept of the fitted line."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:15
msgid "`slope_std`: incertezza standard sulla pendenza."
msgstr "`slope_std`: standard uncertainty on the slope."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:16
msgid "`intercept_std`: incertezza standard sull'intercetta."
msgstr "`intercept_std`: standard uncertainty on the intercept."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:17
msgid "`covariance`: covarianza tra i due parametri del fit."
msgstr "`covariance`: covariance between the two fit parameters."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:18
msgid "`correlation`: coefficiente di correlazione tra pendenza e intercetta."
msgstr "`correlation`: correlation coefficient between slope and intercept."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:19
msgid "`residuals`: vettore dei residui `y - (m x + c)`."
msgstr "`residuals`: vector of residuals `y - (m x + c)`."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:20
msgid "`residual_std`: stima sintetica della dispersione dei residui."
msgstr "`residual_std`: compact estimate of residual dispersion."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:21
msgid "`chi2`: chi quadrato del fit."
msgstr "`chi2`: chi-squared of the fit."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:22
msgid "`reduced_chi2`: chi quadrato ridotto."
msgstr "`reduced_chi2`: reduced chi-squared."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:23
msgid "`dof`: gradi di liberta, pari a `n - 2`."
msgstr "`dof`: degrees of freedom, equal to `n - 2`."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:24
msgid "`iterations`: numero di aggiornamenti dei pesi effettuati."
msgstr "`iterations`: number of weight updates performed."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:25
msgid ""
"`converged`: indica se l'iterazione con `sigma_x` ha soddisfatto il criterio di "
"arresto."
msgstr ""
"`converged`: indicates whether the iteration with `sigma_x` satisfied the stopping "
"criterion."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:26
msgid "`figure`: oggetto matplotlib oppure `None` se `show_plot=False`."
msgstr "`figure`: matplotlib object or `None` when `show_plot=False`."

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:28
msgid "Quando leggerlo"
msgstr "When to read it"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:30
msgid "Usa questo oggetto quando vuoi:"
msgstr "Use this object when you want to:"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:32
msgid "recuperare i parametri del fit senza dover parsare una stringa o una legenda"
msgstr "retrieve the fit parameters without having to parse a string or a legend"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:33
msgid "controllare la qualita del fit tramite residui e `reduced_chi2`"
msgstr "check fit quality through residuals and `reduced_chi2`"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:34
msgid "decidere se salvare o riusare la figura generata"
msgstr "decide whether to save or reuse the generated figure"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:36
msgid "Esempio"
msgstr "Example"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:46
msgid "Note"
msgstr "Notes"

#: ../../source/moduli/fit_utils/linear-fit-result.md:48
msgid ""
"La classe non esegue calcoli da sola: e una rappresentazione dell'output prodotto da "
"[`lin_fit`](lin-fit.md)."
msgstr ""
"The class does not perform calculations on its own: it is a representation of the "
"output produced by [`lin_fit`](lin-fit.md)."

